705459f-a.title: Brooklyn: Lincoln Avenue - Linden Boulevard
705459f-a.text:
Lincoln Ave., east side, between Linden Boulevard and Lorraine Ave..
showing a farmhouse that is designated as 546 Sheridan Ave., which is Barallel
to Lincoln Ave., and to the right of the farmhouse.
April 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
